                <head/>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The paper reports that there are 23 married couples in Staunton who have
                    not had children. "While there is life there is hope."</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>01</column>
                <head>The Work Begun</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The paper reports that the harvest began last week in the Staunton area. By
                    all reports, it will be the largest wheat crop ever gathered in the Valley.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
