            <div type="a">
                <column>02</column>
                <head>Staunton</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The paper praises Staunton's central location, and touts its schools and
                    institutions such as the Western Lunatic Asylum; the Institution for the Deaf,
                    Dumb, and Blind; the Episcopal, Methodist, and Presbyterian Female Schools; and
                    the many male schools.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
